The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms and fairness in decision-making systems, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of iterative algorithms and convergence guarantees, which are topics in cryptography and security (cs.CR) and systems and control (cs.SI). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed framework on datasets, which could fall under the category of computer systems and networking (cs.CY).
